  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Ever-changing World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Svarog's Dream, the absolute freedom to explore the world and make decisions is yours. However, every action influences the world around you, for better or worse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Soul Lost Between Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start as a lost soul, inhabiting human hosts who are desperate enough to embrace you. With each death, you revisit the underworld to possess a new body from a selection of unique characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Pawn in the Game of Gods</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While humans wage their wars on Earth, the Gods clash against each other in the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even with their immense power, they search for a means to gain momentum in their eternal battles. All existence is bound by the threads of destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Except for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have the power of free will, a gift the gods will go to great lengths to persuade to their side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004640/extras/48285e558062cea5f3b89545de74d727.avif?t=1762800076\" width=800 height=219 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The old prophecy:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Svarog, the first god, created six worlds and fell asleep.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In his dream, he created the seventh world, Earth.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Once he wakes up, Earth will cease to exist.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embrace a living, responsive world filled with emergent stories, while also experiencing over 100 handcrafted quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat, cook, sleep, craft potions, upgrade gear, buy houses, take loans, and even evade debt collectors or headhunters, among much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own character build using abilities from 12 unique classes, and equip them with hundreds of weapons, armor pieces, and accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004640/extras/ee113f83e6c2183956de3bc329e1948e.avif?t=1762800076\" width=800 height=231 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"We took everything we loved about old-school RPGs and then added a modern twist on top of it all.\"</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Ever-changing World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Svarog's Dream, the absolute freedom to explore the world and make decisions is yours. However, every action influences the world around you, for better or worse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Soul Lost Between Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start as a lost soul, inhabiting human hosts who are desperate enough to embrace you. With each death, you revisit the underworld to possess a new body from a selection of unique characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Pawn in the Game of Gods</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While humans wage their wars on Earth, the Gods clash against each other in the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even with their immense power, they search for a means to gain momentum in their eternal battles. All existence is bound by the threads of destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Except for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have the power of free will, a gift the gods will go to great lengths to persuade to their side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004640/extras/48285e558062cea5f3b89545de74d727.avif?t=1762800076\" width=800 height=219 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The old prophecy:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Svarog, the first god, created six worlds and fell asleep.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In his dream, he created the seventh world, Earth.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Once he wakes up, Earth will cease to exist.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embrace a living, responsive world filled with emergent stories, while also experiencing over 100 handcrafted quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat, cook, sleep, craft potions, upgrade gear, buy houses, take loans, and even evade debt collectors or headhunters, among much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own character build using abilities from 12 unique classes, and equip them with hundreds of weapons, armor pieces, and accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004640/extras/ee113f83e6c2183956de3bc329e1948e.avif?t=1762800076\" width=800 height=231 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"We took everything we loved about old-school RPGs and then added a modern twist on top of it all.\"</i></p>",
